===J. Reuben Clark===
In addition, [[J. Reuben Clark]] was only a member of the Quorum of the Twelve for one week in 1945 and six days in 1951, which were periods of time when the [[First Presidency (LDS Church)|First Presidency]] was dissolved due to the death of the [[President of the Church (LDS Church)|President of the Church]].
